{"word":"ἐξέργω","slug":"ἐξέργω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξέργω</b></el> <el>(attic <el>ἐξ-είργω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to shut out from</i> a place, <i>debar</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἐξείργειν τινα χθονός</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>ἐκ τοῦ θεάτρου</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἐξείργεσθαι πάντων</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to debar, hinder, prevent, preclude</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to force</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be constrained</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}